en_110597_28	After the ordination ceremony, Viharadhipathi of Mangala Maha Viharaya Venerable Seruwila Saranakiththi Thera conducted a discourse.
en_110597_29	After the apprentices were ordained, an alms giving was held for 150 Bhikkus with the participation of Asia Broadcasting corporation Chairman Mr. Rayynor Silva.
